{
  "video_id": "klBwPWL69P8",
  "title": "Ken Goldberg: 4 lessons from robots about being human",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Morton Bast Reviewer: Thu-Huong Ha"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12539.0,
      "end_time": 15358.0,
      "text": "I know this is going to sound strange,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 15382.0,
      "end_time": 20365.0,
      "text": "but I think robots can inspire us to be better humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21245.0,
      "end_time": 24339.0,
      "text": "See, I grew up in Bethlehem, Pennsylvania,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24363.0,
      "end_time": 26301.0,
      "text": "the home of Bethlehem Steel."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26991.0,
      "end_time": 29103.0,
      "text": "My father was an engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 29127.0,
      "end_time": 33446.0,
      "text": "and when I was growing up, he would teach me how things worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33470.0,
      "end_time": 35564.0,
      "text": "We would build projects together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35588.0,
      "end_time": 38356.0,
      "text": "like model rockets and slot cars."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38732.0,
      "end_time": 41640.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the go-kart that we built together."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42208.0,
      "end_time": 43952.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s me behind the wheel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43976.0,
      "end_time": 46200.0,
      "text": "with my sister and my best friend at the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47875.0,
      "end_time": 49801.0,
      "text": "And one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49825.0,
      "end_time": 52908.0,
      "text": "he came home, when I was about 10 years old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52932.0,
      "end_time": 55558.0,
      "text": "and at the dinner table, he announced"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55582.0,
      "end_time": 59294.0,
      "text": "that for our next project,  we were going to build ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 59318.0,
      "end_time": 60468.0,
      "text": "a robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 61604.0,
      "end_time": 62759.0,
      "text": "A robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63120.0,
      "end_time": 65182.0,
      "text": "Now, I was thrilled about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65206.0,
      "end_time": 69900.0,
      "text": "because at school, there was a bully named Kevin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69330.0,
      "end_time": 70922.0,
      "text": "and he was picking on me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70946.0,
      "end_time": 73336.0,
      "text": "because I was the only Jewish kid in class."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 73910.0,
      "end_time": 76283.0,
      "text": "So I couldn&#39;t wait to get started to work on this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76307.0,
      "end_time": 78917.0,
      "text": "so I could introduce Kevin to my robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78941.0,
      "end_time": 79971.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79995.0,
      "end_time": 84238.0,
      "text": "(Robot noises)"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89552.0,
      "end_time": 90944.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90968.0,
      "end_time": 94817.0,
      "text": "But that wasn&#39;t the kind of robot my dad had in mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94841.0,
      "end_time": 95908.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95933.0,
      "end_time": 99565.0,
      "text": "See, he owned a chromium-plating company,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99589.0,
      "end_time": 105462.0,
      "text": "and they had to move heavy steel parts between tanks of chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105486.0,
      "end_time": 108859.0,
      "text": "And so he needed an industrial robot like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108883.0,
      "end_time": 110985.0,
      "text": "that could basically do the heavy lifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111684.0,
      "end_time": 115274.0,
      "text": "But my dad didn&#39;t get the kind of robot he wanted, either."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 115870.0,
      "end_time": 118300.0,
      "text": "He and I worked on it for several years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118324.0,
      "end_time": 123690.0,
      "text": "but it was the 1970s, and the technology that was available to amateurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123930.0,
      "end_time": 124419.0,
      "text": "just wasn&#39;t there yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125992.0,
      "end_time": 128777.0,
      "text": "So Dad continued to do this kind of work by hand."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129595.0,
      "end_time": 131230.0,
      "text": "And a few years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131730.0,
      "end_time": 133305.0,
      "text": "he was diagnosed with cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 135822.0,
      "end_time": 137392.0,
      "text": "You see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 137416.0,
      "end_time": 140120.0,
      "text": "what the robot we were trying to build was telling him"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140360.0,
      "end_time": 142192.0,
      "text": "was not about doing the heavy lifting."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142216.0,
      "end_time": 143367.0,
      "text": "It was a warning"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143391.0,
      "end_time": 145894.0,
      "text": "about his exposure to the toxic chemicals."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 147184.0,
      "end_time": 149477.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t recognize that at the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 149501.0,
      "end_time": 151187.0,
      "text": "and he contracted leukemia."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151827.0,
      "end_time": 153719.0,
      "text": "And he died at the age of 45."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 155354.0,
      "end_time": 157130.0,
      "text": "I was devastated by this."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 157703.0,
      "end_time": 160465.0,
      "text": "And I never forgot the robot that he and I tried to build."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162195.0,
      "end_time": 165748.0,
      "text": "When I was at college, I decided to study engineering, like him."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167810.0,
      "end_time": 171629.0,
      "text": "And I went to Carnegie Mellon, and I earned my PhD in robotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171653.0,
      "end_time": 173561.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been studying robots ever since."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174721.0,
      "end_time": 179316.0,
      "text": "So what I&#39;d like to tell you about are four robot projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179340.0,
      "end_time": 182389.0,
      "text": "and how they&#39;ve inspired me to be a better human."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 186206.0,
      "end_time": 191820.0,
      "text": "By 1993, I was a young professor at USC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191844.0,
      "end_time": 194662.0,
      "text": "and I was just building up my own robotics lab,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194686.0,
      "end_time": 197907.0,
      "text": "and this was the year the World Wide Web came out."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 198487.0,
      "end_time": 201472.0,
      "text": "And I remember my students were the ones who told me about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 201496.0,
      "end_time": 203813.0,
      "text": "and we would -- we were just amazed."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 203837.0,
      "end_time": 207220.0,
      "text": "We started playing with this, and that afternoon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207244.0,
      "end_time": 211522.0,
      "text": "we realized that we could use this new, universal interface"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 211546.0,
      "end_time": 215974.0,
      "text": "to allow anyone in the world to operate the robot in our lab."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 217339.0,
      "end_time": 221381.0,
      "text": "So, rather than have it fight or do industrial work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 222413.0,
      "end_time": 224943.0,
      "text": "we decided to build a planter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 224967.0,
      "end_time": 226918.0,
      "text": "put the robot into the center of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226942.0,
      "end_time": 228620.0,
      "text": "and we called it the Telegarden."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 229736.0,
      "end_time": 234253.0,
      "text": "And we had put a camera in the gripper of the hand of the robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 234277.0,
      "end_time": 237208.0,
      "text": "and we wrote some special scripts and software,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 237232.0,
      "end_time": 239266.0,
      "text": "so that anyone in the world could come in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 239290.0,
      "end_time": 241730.0,
      "text": "and by clicking on the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 241980.0,
      "end_time": 244719.0,
      "text": "they could move the robot around and visit the garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 245416.0,
      "end_time": 249267.0,
      "text": "But we also set up some other software"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 249291.0,
      "end_time": 253207.0,
      "text": "that lets you participate and help us water the garden, remotely."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 253643.0,
      "end_time": 255932.0,
      "text": "And if you watered it a few times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 255956.0,
      "end_time": 258231.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d give you your own seed to plant."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 259166.0,
      "end_time": 262643.0,
      "text": "Now, this was an engineering project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 262667.0,
      "end_time": 266779.0,
      "text": "and we published some papers on the system design of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 266803.0,
      "end_time": 269448.0,
      "text": "but we also thought of it as an art installation."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 270638.0,
      "end_time": 272787.0,
      "text": "It was invited, after the first year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 272811.0,
      "end_time": 275830.0,
      "text": "by the Ars Electronica Museum in Austria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 275855.0,
      "end_time": 278677.0,
      "text": "to have it installed in their lobby."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 279558.0,
      "end_time": 283545.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m happy to say, it remained online there, 24 hours a day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 283569.0,
      "end_time": 285400.0,
      "text": "for almost nine years."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 286369.0,
      "end_time": 290144.0,
      "text": "That robot was operated by more people"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 290168.0,
      "end_time": 292650.0,
      "text": "than any other robot in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 293303.0,
      "end_time": 294930.0,
      "text": "Now, one day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 294954.0,
      "end_time": 298302.0,
      "text": "I got a call out of the blue from a student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 299211.0,
      "end_time": 303369.0,
      "text": "who asked a very simple but profound question."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 304361.0,
      "end_time": 307187.0,
      "text": "He said, \"Is the robot real?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 308599.0,
      "end_time": 310885.0,
      "text": "Now, everyone else had assumed it was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 310909.0,
      "end_time": 313425.0,
      "text": "and we knew it was, because we were working with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 313449.0,
      "end_time": 314847.0,
      "text": "But I knew what he meant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 314871.0,
      "end_time": 316313.0,
      "text": "because it would be possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 316337.0,
      "end_time": 319122.0,
      "text": "to take a bunch of pictures of flowers in a garden"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 319146.0,
      "end_time": 322785.0,
      "text": "and then, basically, index them in a computer system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 322809.0,
      "end_time": 325436.0,
      "text": "such that it would appear that there was a real robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 325460.0,
      "end_time": 326609.0,
      "text": "when there wasn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 327880.0,
      "end_time": 328612.0,
      "text": "And the more I thought about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 328636.0,
      "end_time": 332215.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t think of a good answer for how he could tell the difference."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 332628.0,
      "end_time": 335425.0,
      "text": "This was right about the time that I was offered a position"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 335449.0,
      "end_time": 336750.0,
      "text": "here at Berkeley."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 336774.0,
      "end_time": 338419.0,
      "text": "And when I got here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 338443.0,
      "end_time": 340805.0,
      "text": "I looked up Hubert Dreyfus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 340829.0,
      "end_time": 343756.0,
      "text": "who&#39;s a world-renowned professor of philosophy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 344582.0,
      "end_time": 347312.0,
      "text": "And I talked with him about this and he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 347336.0,
      "end_time": 351438.0,
      "text": "\"This is one of the oldest and most central problems in philosophy."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 351462.0,
      "end_time": 355479.0,
      "text": "It goes back to the Skeptics and up through Descartes."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 355503.0,
      "end_time": 358685.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the issue of epistemology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 358709.0,
      "end_time": 361577.0,
      "text": "the study of how do we know that something is true.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 362625.0,
      "end_time": 364625.0,
      "text": "So he and I started working together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 364649.0,
      "end_time": 367520.0,
      "text": "and we coined a new term: \"telepistemology,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 368757.0,
      "end_time": 370893.0,
      "text": "the study of knowledge at a distance."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 371303.0,
      "end_time": 375794.0,
      "text": "We invited leading artists, engineers and philosophers"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 375818.0,
      "end_time": 377137.0,
      "text": "to write essays about this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 377161.0,
      "end_time": 380865.0,
      "text": "and the results are collected in this book from MIT Press."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 381959.0,
      "end_time": 384550.0,
      "text": "So thanks to this student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 384790.0,
      "end_time": 387398.0,
      "text": "who questioned what everyone else had assumed to be true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 387422.0,
      "end_time": 391399.0,
      "text": "this project taught me an important lesson about life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 391423.0,
      "end_time": 394410.0,
      "text": "which is to always question assumptions."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 395807.0,
      "end_time": 397983.0,
      "text": "Now, the second project I&#39;ll tell you about"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 398700.0,
      "end_time": 399999.0,
      "text": "grew out of the Telegarden."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 400230.0,
      "end_time": 402844.0,
      "text": "As it was operating, my students and I were very interested"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 402868.0,
      "end_time": 405209.0,
      "text": "in how people were interacting with each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 405233.0,
      "end_time": 407290.0,
      "text": "and what they were doing with the garden."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 407314.0,
      "end_time": 408465.0,
      "text": "So we started thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 408489.0,
      "end_time": 410457.0,
      "text": "what if the robot could leave the garden"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 410481.0,
      "end_time": 413295.0,
      "text": "and go out into some other interesting environment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 413319.0,
      "end_time": 416600.0,
      "text": "Like, for example, what if it could go to a dinner party"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 416840.0,
      "end_time": 417545.0,
      "text": "at the White House?"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 417569.0,
      "end_time": 419680.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 420401.0,
      "end_time": 423970.0,
      "text": "So, because we were interested more in the system design"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 423994.0,
      "end_time": 426937.0,
      "text": "and the user interface than in the hardware,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 426961.0,
      "end_time": 428112.0,
      "text": "we decided that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 428136.0,
      "end_time": 432623.0,
      "text": "rather than have a robot replace the human to go to the party,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 432647.0,
      "end_time": 434877.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d have a human replace the robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 435679.0,
      "end_time": 437138.0,
      "text": "We called it the Tele-Actor."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 437978.0,
      "end_time": 439986.0,
      "text": "We got a human,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 440100.0,
      "end_time": 443118.0,
      "text": "someone who&#39;s very outgoing and gregarious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 443142.0,
      "end_time": 447397.0,
      "text": "and she was outfitted with a helmet with various equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 447421.0,
      "end_time": 448705.0,
      "text": "cameras and microphones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 448729.0,
      "end_time": 451794.0,
      "text": "and then a backpack with wireless Internet connection."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 452882.0,
      "end_time": 455260.0,
      "text": "And the idea was that she could go"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 455500.0,
      "end_time": 457500.0,
      "text": "into a remote and interesting environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 457524.0,
      "end_time": 459541.0,
      "text": "and then over the Internet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 459565.0,
      "end_time": 462157.0,
      "text": "people could experience what she was experiencing."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 462736.0,
      "end_time": 465707.0,
      "text": "So they could see what she was seeing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 465731.0,
      "end_time": 469140.0,
      "text": "but then, more importantly, they could participate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 469380.0,
      "end_time": 473788.0,
      "text": "by interacting with each other and coming up with ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 473812.0,
      "end_time": 477781.0,
      "text": "about what she should do next and where she should go,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 477805.0,
      "end_time": 480110.0,
      "text": "and then conveying those to the Tele-Actor."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 481690.0,
      "end_time": 483490.0,
      "text": "So we got a chance to take the Tele-Actor"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 483514.0,
      "end_time": 486322.0,
      "text": "to the Webby Awards in San Francisco."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 487129.0,
      "end_time": 490369.0,
      "text": "And that year, Sam Donaldson was the host."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 492290.0,
      "end_time": 494980.0,
      "text": "Just before the curtain went up, I had about 30 seconds"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 495400.0,
      "end_time": 498746.0,
      "text": "to explain to Mr. Donaldson what we were going to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 500119.0,
      "end_time": 503636.0,
      "text": "And I said, \"The Tele-Actor is going to be joining you onstage."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 503660.0,
      "end_time": 506140.0,
      "text": "This is a new experimental project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 506380.0,
      "end_time": 508633.0,
      "text": "and people are watching her on their screens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 508657.0,
      "end_time": 511948.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s cameras involved and there&#39;s microphones"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 511972.0,
      "end_time": 513757.0,
      "text": "and she&#39;s got an earbud in her ear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 513782.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516990.00000000006,
      "text": "and people over the network are giving her advice"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 516123.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517281.00000000006,
      "text": "about what to do next.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 517304.0,
      "end_time": 518699.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"Wait a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 519806.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520979.00000000006,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I do.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 521299.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525980.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526400.0,
      "end_time": 527876.0,
      "text": "So he loved the concept,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 527900.0,
      "end_time": 532153.0,
      "text": "and when the Tele-Actor walked onstage, she walked right up to him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 532177.0,
      "end_time": 534636.0,
      "text": "and she gave him a big kiss right on the lips."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 534660.0,
      "end_time": 536612.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 536636.0,
      "end_time": 539558.0,
      "text": "We were totally surprised -- we had no idea that would happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 539582.0,
      "end_time": 542200.0,
      "text": "And he was great, he just gave her a big hug in return,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 542224.0,
      "end_time": 543881.0,
      "text": "and it worked out great."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 543905.0,
      "end_time": 545944.0,
      "text": "But that night, as we were packing up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 545969.0,
      "end_time": 550524.0,
      "text": "I asked the Tele-Actor, how did the Tele-Directors decide"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 550548.0,
      "end_time": 553548.0,
      "text": "that they would give a kiss to Sam Donaldson?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 555135.0,
      "end_time": 556592.0,
      "text": "And she said they hadn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 557274.0,
      "end_time": 559892.0,
      "text": "She said, when she was just about to walk onstage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 559916.0,
      "end_time": 562890.0,
      "text": "the Tele-Directors still were trying to agree on what to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 562914.0,
      "end_time": 566140.0,
      "text": "and so she just walked onstage and did what felt most natural."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 566380.0,
      "end_time": 570552.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 570576.0,
      "end_time": 573668.0,
      "text": "So, the success of the Tele-Actor that night"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 573692.0,
      "end_time": 577945.0,
      "text": "was due to the fact that she was a wonderful actor."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 577969.0,
      "end_time": 580398.0,
      "text": "She knew when to trust her instincts."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 580422.0,
      "end_time": 584351.0,
      "text": "And so that project taught me another lesson about life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584375.0,
      "end_time": 588220.0,
      "text": "which is that, when in doubt, improvise."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 588460.0,
      "end_time": 589712.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 590664.0,
      "end_time": 595583.0,
      "text": "Now, the third project grew out of my experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 595607.0,
      "end_time": 597456.0,
      "text": "when my father was in the hospital."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 599284.0,
      "end_time": 602637.0,
      "text": "He was undergoing a treatment -- chemotherapy treatments --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 602661.0,
      "end_time": 606930.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s a related treatment called brachytherapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 606955.0,
      "end_time": 610743.0,
      "text": "where tiny, radioactive seeds are placed into the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 610767.0,
      "end_time": 612501.0,
      "text": "to treat cancerous tumors."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 613572.0,
      "end_time": 615843.0,
      "text": "And the way it&#39;s done, as you can see here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 615867.0,
      "end_time": 620233.0,
      "text": "is that surgeons insert needles into the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 620258.0,
      "end_time": 621573.0,
      "text": "to deliver the seeds."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 621974.0,
      "end_time": 625672.0,
      "text": "And all these needles are inserted in parallel."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 626445.0,
      "end_time": 631838.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s very common that some of the needles penetrate sensitive organs."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 632635.0,
      "end_time": 639608.0,
      "text": "And as a result, the needles damage these organs, cause damage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 639632.0,
      "end_time": 642400.0,
      "text": "which leads to trauma and side effects."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 642581.0,
      "end_time": 644225.0,
      "text": "So my students and I wondered:"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 644249.0,
      "end_time": 648771.0,
      "text": "what if we could modify the system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 648795.0,
      "end_time": 651420.0,
      "text": "so that the needles could come in at different angles?"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 652395.0,
      "end_time": 654238.0,
      "text": "So we simulated this;"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 654262.0,
      "end_time": 657707.0,
      "text": "we developed some optimization algorithms and we simulated this."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 657731.0,
      "end_time": 658882.0,
      "text": "And we were able to show"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 658906.0,
      "end_time": 661468.0,
      "text": "that we are able to avoid the delicate organs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 661492.0,
      "end_time": 666545.0,
      "text": "and yet still achieve the coverage of the tumors with the radiation."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 667313.0,
      "end_time": 670787.0,
      "text": "So now, we&#39;re working with doctors at UCSF"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 670811.0,
      "end_time": 673780.0,
      "text": "and engineers at Johns Hopkins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 673102.0,
      "end_time": 677640.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re building a robot that has a number of --"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 677880.0,
      "end_time": 679687.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a specialized design with different joints"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 679711.0,
      "end_time": 684340.0,
      "text": "that can allow the needles to come in at an infinite variety of angles."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 684483.0,
      "end_time": 688204.0,
      "text": "And as you can see here, they can avoid delicate organs"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 688229.0,
      "end_time": 690893.0,
      "text": "and still reach the targets they&#39;re aiming for."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 692190.0,
      "end_time": 697400.0,
      "text": "So, by questioning this assumption that all the needles have to be parallel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 697280.0,
      "end_time": 699654.0,
      "text": "this project also taught me an important lesson:"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 700114.0,
      "end_time": 704869.0,
      "text": "When in doubt, when your path is blocked, pivot."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 705797.0,
      "end_time": 709637.0,
      "text": "And the last project also has to do with medical robotics."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 710187.0,
      "end_time": 713757.0,
      "text": "And this is something that&#39;s grown out of a system"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 713781.0,
      "end_time": 717128.0,
      "text": "called the da Vinci surgical robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 717866.0,
      "end_time": 720310.0,
      "text": "And this is a commercially available device."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 720334.0,
      "end_time": 723306.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s being used in over 2,000 hospitals around the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 724130.0,
      "end_time": 728386.0,
      "text": "The idea is it allows the surgeon to operate comfortably"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 728410.0,
      "end_time": 730187.0,
      "text": "in his own coordinate frame."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 732762.0,
      "end_time": 738531.0,
      "text": "Many of the subtasks in surgery are very routine and tedious, like suturing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 738555.0,
      "end_time": 740822.0,
      "text": "and currently, all of these are performed"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 740846.0,
      "end_time": 744713.0,
      "text": "under the specific and immediate control of the surgeon."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 745374.0,
      "end_time": 747642.0,
      "text": "So the surgeon becomes fatigued over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 748860.0,
      "end_time": 749522.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;ve been wondering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 749546.0,
      "end_time": 753917.0,
      "text": "what if we could program the robot to perform some of these subtasks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 753941.0,
      "end_time": 755322.0,
      "text": "and thereby free the surgeon"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 755346.0,
      "end_time": 758581.0,
      "text": "to focus on the more complicated parts of the surgery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 758605.0,
      "end_time": 761405.0,
      "text": "and also cut down on the time that the surgery would take"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 761429.0,
      "end_time": 764268.0,
      "text": "if we could get the robot to do them a little bit faster?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 764958.0,
      "end_time": 768380.0,
      "text": "Now, it&#39;s hard to program a robot to do delicate things like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 768943.0,
      "end_time": 773149.0,
      "text": "But it turns out my colleague Pieter Abbeel, who&#39;s here at Berkeley,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 773173.0,
      "end_time": 778653.0,
      "text": "has developed a new set of techniques for teaching robots from example."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 779170.0,
      "end_time": 781913.0,
      "text": "So he&#39;s gotten robots to fly helicopters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 781937.0,
      "end_time": 785191.0,
      "text": "do incredibly interesting, beautiful acrobatics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 785215.0,
      "end_time": 787182.0,
      "text": "by watching human experts fly them."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 788152.0,
      "end_time": 790580.0,
      "text": "So we got one of these robots."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 790820.0,
      "end_time": 792622.0,
      "text": "We started working with Pieter and his students."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 792646.0,
      "end_time": 796825.0,
      "text": "And we asked a surgeon to perform a task --"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 798761.0,
      "end_time": 799911.0,
      "text": "with the robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 799936.0,
      "end_time": 802961.0,
      "text": "So what we&#39;re doing is asking the surgeon to perform the task,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 802985.0,
      "end_time": 805210.0,
      "text": "and we record the motions of the robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 805450.0,
      "end_time": 806471.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 806495.0,
      "end_time": 809616.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll use tracing out a figure eight as an example."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 810170.0,
      "end_time": 813804.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s what it looks like when the robot --"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 813828.0,
      "end_time": 816896.0,
      "text": "this is what the robot&#39;s path looks like, those three examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 816920.0,
      "end_time": 821550.0,
      "text": "Now, those are much better than what a novice like me could do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 821800.0,
      "end_time": 823774.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re still jerky and imprecise."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 823798.0,
      "end_time": 826739.0,
      "text": "So we record all these examples, the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 826763.0,
      "end_time": 829624.0,
      "text": "and then go through a sequence of steps."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 830278.0,
      "end_time": 833404.0,
      "text": "First, we use a technique called dynamic time warping"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 833428.0,
      "end_time": 834918.0,
      "text": "from speech recognition."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 834942.0,
      "end_time": 838279.0,
      "text": "And this allows us to temporally align all of the examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 838918.0,
      "end_time": 844120.0,
      "text": "And then we apply Kalman filtering, a technique from control theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 844144.0,
      "end_time": 847113.0,
      "text": "that allows us to statistically analyze all the noise"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 847137.0,
      "end_time": 851258.0,
      "text": "and extract the desired trajectory that underlies them."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 853283.0,
      "end_time": 855833.0,
      "text": "Now we take those human demonstrations --"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 855857.0,
      "end_time": 857531.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re all noisy and imperfect --"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 857556.0,
      "end_time": 860154.0,
      "text": "and we extract from them an inferred task trajectory"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 860178.0,
      "end_time": 862704.0,
      "text": "and control sequence for the robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 863181.0,
      "end_time": 865497.0,
      "text": "We then execute that on the robot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 865521.0,
      "end_time": 867545.0,
      "text": "we observe what happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 867570.0,
      "end_time": 868927.0,
      "text": "then we adjust the controls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 868951.0,
      "end_time": 871747.0,
      "text": "using a sequence of techniques called iterative learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 873129.0,
      "end_time": 876538.0,
      "text": "Then what we do is we increase the velocity a little bit."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 877244.0,
      "end_time": 880379.0,
      "text": "We observe the results, adjust the controls again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 881340.0,
      "end_time": 883112.0,
      "text": "and observe what happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 883136.0,
      "end_time": 885303.0,
      "text": "And we go through this several rounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 885327.0,
      "end_time": 886508.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s the result."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 886968.0,
      "end_time": 888706.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the inferred task trajectory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 888730.0,
      "end_time": 891951.0,
      "text": "and here&#39;s the robot moving at the speed of the human."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 891975.0,
      "end_time": 894800.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s four times the speed of the human."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 894477.0,
      "end_time": 895961.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s seven times."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 897400.0,
      "end_time": 901829.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s the robot operating at 10 times the speed of the human."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 902762.0,
      "end_time": 905662.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re able to get a robot to perform a delicate task"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 905687.0,
      "end_time": 908573.0,
      "text": "like a surgical subtask,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 909810.0,
      "end_time": 910962.0,
      "text": "at 10 times the speed of a human."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 912185.0,
      "end_time": 914444.0,
      "text": "So this project also,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 914469.0,
      "end_time": 916994.0,
      "text": "because of its involved practicing and learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 917180.0,
      "end_time": 918780.0,
      "text": "doing something over and over again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 918804.0,
      "end_time": 921381.0,
      "text": "this project also has a lesson, which is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 921405.0,
      "end_time": 923809.0,
      "text": "if you want to do something well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 925840.0,
      "end_time": 929524.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no substitute for practice, practice, practice."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 933186.0,
      "end_time": 936673.0,
      "text": "So these are four of the lessons that I&#39;ve learned from robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 936697.0,
      "end_time": 937995.0,
      "text": "over the years."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 939312.0,
      "end_time": 944819.0,
      "text": "And the field of robotics has gotten much better over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 946319.0,
      "end_time": 948594.0,
      "text": "Nowadays, high school students can build robots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 948619.0,
      "end_time": 951503.0,
      "text": "like the industrial robot my dad and I tried to build."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 952675.0,
      "end_time": 955444.0,
      "text": "But, it&#39;s very -- now ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 955954.0,
      "end_time": 959255.0,
      "text": "And now, I have a daughter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 959857.0,
      "end_time": 961140.0,
      "text": "named Odessa."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 961673.0,
      "end_time": 962926.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s eight years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 963682.0,
      "end_time": 965331.0,
      "text": "And she likes robots, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 965970.0,
      "end_time": 967366.0,
      "text": "Maybe it runs in the family."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 967390.0,
      "end_time": 968630.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 968654.0,
      "end_time": 970749.0,
      "text": "I wish she could meet my dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 972303.0,
      "end_time": 975430.0,
      "text": "And now I get to teach her how things work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 975670.0,
      "end_time": 977297.0,
      "text": "and we get to build projects together."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 977321.0,
      "end_time": 980527.0,
      "text": "And I wonder what kind of lessons she&#39;ll learn from them."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 982147.0,
      "end_time": 986154.0,
      "text": "Robots are the most human of our machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 986983.0,
      "end_time": 989936.0,
      "text": "They can&#39;t solve all of the world&#39;s problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 989961.0,
      "end_time": 993484.0,
      "text": "but I think they have something important to teach us."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 994276.0,
      "end_time": 996276.0,
      "text": "I invite all of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 996301.0,
      "end_time": 999879.0,
      "text": "to think about the innovations that you&#39;re interested in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 1000710.0,
      "end_time": 1002953.0,
      "text": "the machines that you wish for."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 1003660.0,
      "end_time": 1006266.0,
      "text": "And think about what they might be telling you."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 1007210.0,
      "end_time": 1010955.0,
      "text": "Because I have a hunch that many of our technological innovations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 1010980.0,
      "end_time": 1012651.0,
      "text": "the devices we dream about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 1014170.0,
      "end_time": 1017154.0,
      "text": "can inspire us to be better humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 1017980.0,
      "end_time": 1019131.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 1019160.0,
      "end_time": 1021711.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}